Detailed Description

cvmx_l2c_tad::_timeout

This register records error information for an LFBTO (LFB TimeOut). The first LFBTO error will lock the register until the logged error type s cleared. If multiple LFBs timed out simultaneously, then this will contain the information form the lowest LFB number that has timed-out. The address can be for the original transaction address or the replacement address (if both could have timed out, then the transaction address will be here).
